title: Grateful Dead Live at UIC Pavilion on 1987-04-11
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.8 MHz) >KORG AudioGate 4 > Samplitude Pro X3 Suite > FLAC/24
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket, Sugaree, Minglewood Blues, Loser, Tons Of Steel, Desolation Row, Big Railroad Blues, The Music Never Stopped

Set 2

Touch Of Grey, Women Are Smarter, Terrapin Station-> Drums-> Space-> Truckin'-> Wharf Rat-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: Black Muddy River

FM Broadcast WXRT

reviews.review_text: More Charlie Miller magic. Excellent sound, pretty good show.
